private EuclideElement createNewFreePoint(math.geom2d.Point2D point,
                                          EuclideSheetView view)
return either a new free point, or a new point on a curve. If distance to closest curve is 'small enough', create a PointOnLine or PointOnCircle object, initialized with positon given as parameter. Otherwise, return a new Free point.
